<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.9.3">
<l>aṇṭamumiv valaikaṭalu mavaṉikaḷu mellā mamutuceyta tiruvayiṟṟa ṉaraṉkoṇṭu tiriyum</l>
<l>muṇṭamatu niṟaittavaṉkaṇ cāpamatu nīkkum mutalvaṉavaṉ makiḻntiṉitu maruviyuṟai kōyil</l>
<l>eṇṭicaiyum peruñcenne liḷanteṅku katali yilaikkoṭiyoṇ kulaikkamuko ṭikalivaḷam coriya</l>
<l>vaṇṭupala vicaipāṭa mayilālu nāṅkūr vaikunta viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship in Vaikunta Viṇṇakaram in Nānkūr where peacocks call</l>
<l rend="indent">as bees sing many melodies, while in the eight directions</l>
<l>Enlarged red paddy, young cocoanuts, bananas, [betel] leaf creepers,</l>
<l rend="indent">and shining areca nut clusters shower bounty in rivalry,</l>
<l>The temple where dwells the primal [lord], happily with affection [and] rejoicing,</l>
<l rend="indent">who, filling the skull with which Hara wandered,</l>
<l rend="indent">removed the curse on him,</l>
<l>The one whose divine belly made food of the universe,</l>
<l rend="indent">this crashing sea, and all the worlds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
